---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="REQUEST A FACT SHEET | ACHI Studio" description="Request details on our textile sustainability, materials audit, and supply chains.">
  <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl tracking-widest uppercase text-brand-charcoal">FACT SHEET</h1>
      <p class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-gray-400 mt-2 font-light">Transparency & Sourcing Details</p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-sm font-light text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        At ACHI, we values transparency. Our materials, audited suppliers, and fabric sustainability certifications are detailed in our seasonal Corporate Fact Sheet.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-sm space-y-4">
        <h3 class="font-serif text-xs uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold text-brand-charcoal">Request PDF Copy</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
          Please contact our customer support team directly on Line Official <a href="https://line.me" class="underline font-medium hover:text-brand-gold">@achistudio</a> or write to <span class="font-medium text-brand-charcoal">transparency@achi.com</span> to receive our latest auditing report.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
